":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Authorship and blogs and publication.","text":"Most Driven Books\n\nRuchi is the author of several best-selling books that have inspired and empowered entrepreneurs and business leaders worldwide.\n\nContributed Articles and Blogs\n\nHer insightful articles and thought-leadership pieces have been featured in leading publications, further solidifying her position as an industry authority.\n\nDigital Content\n\nIn addition to her books, Ruchi regularly produces a range of digital content, including e-books, whitepapers, and online courses.","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T16:47:17.830Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T18:23:56.596Z"},{"id":"uuxr4r6l5vayypz","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"LET'S CONNECT ON A FREE DISCOVERY SESSION. ","text":"Personal Discovery calls\n\nRuchi offers one-on-one executive coaching to help C-suite leaders and senior executives unlock their full potential, overcome challenges, and drive organizational success.\n\nEntrepreneurial Mentorship\n\nHer entrepreneurial coaching programs provide aspiring and established business owners with the guidance, resources, and accountability they need to scale their ventures.\n\nGroup Coaching Programs\n\nRuchi also facilitates transformative group coaching programs, fostering peer-to-peer learning and synergistic growth among participants.","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T16:47:18.166Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T18:23:56.599Z"},{"id":"8zcqu5ldtaajwig","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Do you know how The science of belief works?","text":"","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T16:47:18.564Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T18:40:11.341Z"},{"id":"3ljlxcb0wq7zatp","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Are you surrounded by Toxic people? them better find Mastermind of driven people.","text":"","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T18:32:07.496Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T18:40:11.349Z"},{"id":"nvf3r71b09p4bcb","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Comfort zone makes life miserable leads to stagnancy. ","text":"","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T18:32:07.489Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T18:40:10.565Z"},{"id":"yu6rj9flb1lvug1","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Connect her to join her International Extraordinary Mastermind to Find true purpose of your life and have a solid vision and mission of life and avail bonus to join her live event.","text":"Phone:\n\n+91 (759) 72-88884\n\nEmail:\n\nruchinilamdoctor@gmail.com\n\nWebsite:\n\nwww.ruchidoctor.com\n\nLinkedIn:\n\nlinkedin.com/in/ruchidoctor","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T16:47:18.431Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T18:40:11.351Z"},{"id":"e1njeqbq66rk5z5","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Social Media Presence and Influence","text":"LinkedIn\n\nConnect with Ruchi on LinkedIn to stay up-to-date on her latest insights and industry news.\n\nTwitter\n\nFollow Ruchi on Twitter for inspiring quotes, entrepreneurial tips, and real-time updates.\n\nInstagram\n\nEngage with Ruchi's visually captivating content on Instagram, where she shares her journey and lifestyle.\n\nYouTube\n\nSubscribe to Ruchi's YouTube channel for exclusive videos, workshops, and masterclasses.ruchidoctor","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T16:47:18.339Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T20:38:59.452Z"},{"id":"c68lkn7z3wca46o","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Coaching is revolution in education, can help you faster forward your life.-Ruchi","text":"","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T17:47:02.947Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T20:52:37.499Z"},{"id":"ek7yyqn4wb5dp0w","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"COACHING IS 21st CENTURIES REVOLUTION IN EDUCATION.- RUCHI","text":"Keynote Addresses\n\nRuchi has been invited to deliver keynote speeches at numerous industry conferences, summits, and corporate events, sharing her insights and strategies for success.\n\nRuchi's Groundbreaking seminars that are driven towards creating transformation!\n\nThe secret Millionaire FrameworkA legendary seminar that is changing lives of millions.!  It's a State of believes that make things possible. \n\nThe Possibilist CodeHow to rewire yourself for an Extraordinary outcomes and strategies to generate possibilities.\n\nSticability without GlueThe power of Persuasion.Her explanation is simple yet powerful to absorb, apply and Stick to your decisions in the highs and lows of life.\n\nAre you looking for a Financial Freedom or Lollipop.Everyone wants financial freedom. But the question is what are you prepared to give up to go up. she helps you to take the escalator of success and makes you feel what does it mean by financial freedom.\n\nAre you looking for Financial Freedom or a Lollipop? by Ruchi Doctor.- Life coach,Leader Entrepreneur\n\nThe Extraordinary you.for those who wants to achieve more. Do more.\n\nRuchi Doctor's Global Mastermind\n\nShe is on a mission to help people to Be an Extraordinary coach. and helps to find their voice which can move the mountain.\n\nPodcast and Zoom Webinar Appearances\n\nRuchi's expertise has also been featured on various podcasts and webinars, where she shares her wealth of knowledge with a broader audience.Her podcast is The Ruchi Doctor Show on spottily.","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T16:47:17.826Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-14T09:15:39.970Z"},{"id":"hsjhhxx9vm1c83r","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"You have to choose between ordinary and Extraordinary. I chose to be one on a mission to help others.-Ruchi ","text":"","previewUrl":null,"createdTime":"2024-10-08T17:41:06.673Z","updatedTime":"2024-10-08T20:56:41.749Z"},{"id":"n1r1g8d9ugqp4p0","archived":false,"docId":"sldxq1hlsh9496r","title":"Hi, My Name is Ruchi Doctor. I am Life coach and Leader Entrepreneur. The Person of 21st century born in 20th century IN 20TH CENTURY. ","text":"Ruchi has he